h4 Params

p The historic gauge is derived from the normal gauge, and thus has all it's params, with differences on the following:

table.params-table
    tr
        td param
        td type
        td default
        td description
    tr
        td max_val
        td Number
        td 1
        td Maximum value
    tr
        td min_val
        td Number
        td 0
        td Minimum value
    tr
        td vertical
        td Boolean
        td false
        td Make the bar vertical (true) or horizontal (false)
    tr
        td color
        td String (from Subtle.COLORS, hex or rgb)
        td COLORS['primary']
        td Main color
    tr
        td smooth
        td Boolean
        td false
        td Makes a smooth transition between updates
    tr
        td border_radius
        td Number
        td 10
        td Bar's border radius (in pixels)
    tr
        td bar_width
        td Number
        td 30
        td Bar's width (in pixels)
    tr
        td font_size
        td Number
        td 15
        td Label's font size
    tr
        td show_label
        td Boolean
        td true
        td Shows a label with the value inside the bar
    tr
        td units
        td String
        td ""
        td Shows units on the label
    tr
        td rounding
        td Number
        td 2
        td Decimal place for rounding


